---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<header class="grid grid-cols-1 l:grid-cols-2 gap-0 bg-white">
  <div class="visual h-screen sticky top-0 flex items-center justify-center">
    <!-- <div class="animation w-1/2 aspect-square z-10"></div> -->
    <img class="centered z-20" src="../assets/images/logo-jdr-02-outline.svg" />
    <img
      class="w-full h-full absolute top-0 object-cover mix-blend-multiply z-10"
      src="./assets/images/portret-jeff-halftone.png"
      alt="Jeff"
    />
    <video
      class="z-1"
      src="../assets/video/03-test.mp4"
      autoplay
      loop
      playsinline
      muted></video>
  </div>

  <div class="item intro p-vw-8 py-vw-16">
    <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight tw">
      I'm a dedicated film producer fueled by a passion for bringing compelling
      stories to the screen. I thrive on diverse storytelling methods, welcoming
      every avenue that leads to inspiration.
    </p>
    <p class="text-2xl mt-vw-8 tw">
      In film production, I turn creative ideas into impactful narratives. From
      consultancy to full-scale production, I specialize in documentaries,
      commercials, and films, overseeing projects from concept to completion.
    </p>
    <p class="text-1xl mt-vw-8 tw">
      Ready to bring your vision to life? Contact me for consultations,
      concepts, and collaboration. Email me anytime to kickstart our creative
      journey!
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/jeffreyderoode/"
        rel="noopener"
        target="_blank">peek!</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  header {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
    z-index: 10;
    transition: all var(--easing-nav-out);
  }

  .visual {
    background: var(--bg);
    z-index: 10;
    transition: all var(--easing-nav-out);
  }

  .animation {
    background: url(./assets/images/logo-jdr-sprite.svg) no-repeat 0 0;
    background-size: 100%;
    animation: sprite 0.5s steps(4) infinite;
    /* z-index: 2; */
  }

  @keyframes sprite {
    from {
      background-position: 0 0;
    }
    to {
      background-position: 0 100%;
    }
  }

  video {
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .centered {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    text-align: center;
    height: 60%;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    header {
      min-height: 100vh;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
